### User-Roles Assignment API Manual Test Collection

@base = http://localhost:3000/api
@auth = Bearer {{token}}

### Asignar rol a usuario
POST {{base}}/user-roles
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{auth}}

{
  "user_id": 1,
  "role_id": 2
}
###

### Listar roles de un usuario
GET {{base}}/user-roles/roles/1
Authorization: {{auth}}
###

### Listar usuarios por nombre de rol
GET {{base}}/user-roles/users/artist
Authorization: {{auth}}
###

### Remover rol de usuario
DELETE {{base}}/user-roles/1/2
Authorization: {{auth}}
###

